name: Hatur Nuhun
description:
Hatur Nuhun is a thank you sentence in Sundanese. usually used to say to someone if they have been helped or helped, and now, I say Hatur Nuhun to all of you who until now have helped me and supported me. I owe you all a lot :) 

3000 x 3000 px, 300 Dpi 
Digital Illustration 
By @zandista_
